skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: name the show
des: This is a game for anyone that watches television. We will give you the name of an actor, and you have to tell us which show we are thinking of. Easy, right? It's harder than you think. If you run into trouble, you can always purchase hints, which will give you a second or third actor from the same show as clues. Think you know television? Good luck!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
